#: resources/assets/js/general/GeneralSettingsTab.tsx:96
msgid "Review intervals"
msgstr "Granskningsintervall"

#: resources/assets/js/general/GeneralSettingsTab.tsx:97
msgid "How often pages must be reviewed and when reminders go out."
msgstr "Hur ofta sidor ska granskas och när påminnelser skickas."

#: resources/assets/js/general/GeneralSettingsTab.tsx:110
msgid "Default review interval (days)"
msgstr "Standardgranskningsintervall (dagar)"

#: resources/assets/js/general/GeneralSettingsTab.tsx:111
msgid "Used when a page has no rule of its own."
msgstr "Används när en sida saknar egen regel."

#: resources/assets/js/general/GeneralSettingsTab.tsx:137
msgid "Notify days before"
msgstr "Avisera dagar före"

#: resources/assets/js/general/GeneralSettingsTab.tsx:138
msgid "Window in which a page is \"due soon\"."
msgstr "Fönster då en sida är \"snart dags\"."

#: resources/assets/js/general/GeneralSettingsTab.tsx:159
msgid "Reminders"
msgstr "Påminnelser"

#: resources/assets/js/general/GeneralSettingsTab.tsx:160
msgid ""
"Control repeat emails while a page stays due or overdue. Marking a page "
"reviewed starts a new cycle."
msgstr ""
"Styr upprepade e-postmeddelanden medan en sida är förfallen eller försenad. "
"Att markera en sida granskad startar en ny cykel."

#: resources/assets/js/general/GeneralSettingsTab.tsx:170
msgid "Send reminders after due date"
msgstr "Skicka påminnelser efter förfallodatum"

#: resources/assets/js/general/GeneralSettingsTab.tsx:176
msgid ""
"When off, each page is included in at most one digest per review cycle "
"(until marked reviewed). When on, overdue pages can appear again after the "
"cadence interval."
msgstr ""
"Av: varje sida ingår högst en gång per granskningscykel (tills den "
"markerats granskad). På: försenade sidor kan visas igen efter "
"påminnelseintervallet."

#: resources/assets/js/general/GeneralSettingsTab.tsx:190
msgid "Reminder cadence (days)"
msgstr "Påminnelseintervall (dagar)"

#: resources/assets/js/general/GeneralSettingsTab.tsx:191
msgid ""
"Minimum days before the same overdue page can appear in another digest. "
"Currently tracked per page, not per recipient — see README."
msgstr ""
"Minsta antal dagar innan samma försenade sida kan visas i ett nytt utskick. "
"Spåras per sida, inte per mottagare — se README."

#: resources/assets/js/general/GeneralSettingsTab.tsx:213
msgid ""
"What happens when someone marks a page as reviewed. Plugin review meta is "
"always stored."
msgstr ""
"Vad som händer när någon markerar en sida som granskad. Pluginets "
"granskningsmetadata sparas alltid."

#: resources/assets/js/general/GeneralSettingsTab.tsx:223
msgid "Update WordPress last modified date"
msgstr "Uppdatera WordPress senast ändrad"

#: resources/assets/js/general/GeneralSettingsTab.tsx:229
msgid ""
"Also updates the post's modified timestamp (shown as \"updated\" on the "
"front-end). Does not create a new revision."
msgstr ""
"Uppdaterar även inläggets ändringstidpunkt (visas som \"uppdaterad\" på "
"webbplatsen). Skapar ingen ny revision."

#: resources/assets/js/general/GeneralSettingsTab.tsx:238
msgid "Default recipients"
msgstr "Standardmottagare"

#: resources/assets/js/general/GeneralSettingsTab.tsx:239
msgid ""
"Recipients used as a fallback when no per-page or inherited recipient is "
"set. Email addresses only here for now; per-page rules support users and "
"roles too."
msgstr ""
"Mottagare som reserv när ingen sida- eller ärvd mottagare finns. Endast "
"e-postadresser här för tillfället; sidregler stödjer även användare och "
"roller."

#: resources/assets/js/general/GeneralSettingsTab.tsx:252
msgid "Default recipient emails"
msgstr "Standardmottagare (e-post)"

#: resources/assets/js/general/GeneralSettingsTab.tsx:253
